  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3110547/java-how-to-create-new-entry-key-value",
  "title" : "Java - How to create new Entry (key, value)",
  "body" : "<p>I'd like to create new item that similarly to <code>Util.Map.Entry</code> that will contain the structure <code>key</code>, <code>value</code>.</p>\n\n<p>The problem is that I can't instantiate a <code>Map.Entry</code> because it's an interface. </p>\n\n<p>Does anyone know how to create a new generic key/value object for Map.Entry?</p>\n"
